<br>
Cast a dex buff, and your weapon skill goes up.<br>
Eqiup a weapon with a higher damage rating, and it goes up, one with a lower rating, and it goes down, regardless of how the weapon 'cons' to you.<br>
Gain a level and train in staff skill.. and the value doesnt move.<br>
<br>
Basically, I think the weapon skill is just a value that determines how 'hard' your weapon hits, and does not actually reflect how skillful you are with it.<br>
